This room features 4 different rain intensities with each having its volume automated on the increase of the rain perameter, when the rain is at full intensity thunder is also introduced The wind also uses volume automation for Water parameter increases the amount of water building up with the rains increasing intensity. The time parameter controls the volume levels of the animals. When the parameter is at 180Ëš (Sun) birds are the only animals playing, their volume decreases as the time parameter is adjusted slowly introducing the crickets and frogs whilst replacing birds. Crickets and frogs also have there volume decrease when the rain parameter is increased
All sounds by Oliver Richardson
